{"type": "article", "id": 48936, "title": "羽绒被的柔软保暖特性，都融入了可爱的平面设计里", "description": "圆润友好的品牌标识，加上俏皮风格的卡通简笔画，创造了一个充满想象力的梦幻般的世界。", "date": "2018-01-07T23:28:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 10665, "name": "品牌设计"}, {"id": 46824, "name": "Buffy"}, {"id": 10666, "name": "Pentagram"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180105122357XI36yEgvjFfBeZ4i.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>平面设计公司 Pentagram 最近接手的新项目，是帮助初创羽绒被品牌 Buffy 塑造品牌形象。</p><p><a href=\"https://buffy.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Buffy</a> 创立于纽约，其创始人 Leo Wang 认为这是一个进入床上用品市场的合适时机，越来越多人开始认真对待自己的睡眠状况。<a href=\"https://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/pentagram-creates-a-friendly-identity-to-introduce-the-worlds-most-comfortable-duvet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">但他同时也发现</a>，大多数人对此并没有更进一步的认知，“他们不明白填充物和面料是如何影响睡眠体验的，而当我们与消费者交谈时，他们一直在说，想要的感觉就是沉睡在云端。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105132346z9nH8BkOZ7EDKpPd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105132346tZwpk5zjxGMlVbSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105132348wkxQPApDXVUvZtST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105132350cCZfFeDiMd7ybPGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Leo Wang 的家人有着 50 年的羽绒被制作经验，这也是支撑他此番创业的起点，他希望能够为客户提供终极的睡眠体验，声称是<a href=\"https://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/pentagram-creates-a-friendly-identity-to-introduce-the-worlds-most-comfortable-duvet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“世界上最舒适，最温和的羽绒被”，</a>采用被用于运动服饰的吸湿排汗面料技术，内里的植物纤维填充材料，亦有助于保持棉被轻盈、温暖和透气。</p><p>Pentagram 的工作是帮助 Buffy 突出其产品的柔软度和创新技术，包括品牌标识的创造和包装设计等。设计师试图创造这样一种认知，“当涉及到羽绒被时，没有什么能够像 Buffy 那样给人蓬松舒适的感觉了。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105132843JRSGHpNZ4EfBv3e8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105132856I1mAx7LZHznkhRSe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>羽绒被品牌一般讲故事，多是拿技术领域的内行话说事儿，Buffy 想用更加生动平实的表达方式，来传达其在羽绒被领域的革命性技术。这也是 Pentagram 接这个项目最具挑战性的部分。</p><p>设计师为其定下了平易近人、有趣、独特的品牌调性，将实用性和简洁性结合起来。</p><p>有趣、活泼的个性体现在品牌标识图形上，标识中的字体是在友好度极高的库珀黑体（Cooper Black）的基础结构上调整而来的，圆润的字母形状也是意在突出羽绒被的柔软度，再搭配暖萌的马卡龙色调，更添轻快活泼的调调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105133106HehJ1SrLMqlgamEp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622727\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105133106k97cZIp6XEBjTRo0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801051331061D0mkfr3TeYnU6Gy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105133107T8WlGv7FhxjsRNOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566364\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105133109n7bjWx3g4zCwhpcq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105133110wUoXdETP5Ce97xLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561818\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>除此之外，设计师还为品牌定制绘制了俏皮风格的卡通简笔画，寥寥几笔画出来的形象，描绘了一个围绕 Buffy 羽绒被包裹的暖暖的柔软的世界，也是创造了一个充满想象力的梦幻般的世界。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180105133140H5Voqgm1pAi8y0FD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801051331411qaKyMZ8djftLRcp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665455\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801051333200olGBDrMUXEszhSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018010513334861NfRuvZDLFMmHzI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.creativeboom.com/inspiration/pentagram-creates-a-friendly-identity-to-introduce-the-worlds-most-comfortable-duvet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Creative Boom</a></p>"}